entries.femaleVariant: Not good, V. Not good at all. Flavio's worm-chow and what's worse – my street cred took a hit. And you know there's nothing worth more to a fixer than their cred.
Now that's what I call pro mercwork! Flavio's yappin' my ears off, says he's never met anyone tougher than you.
I'm not the vindictive type, so I'll let this slide. But I've got a good memory – consider this strike one. Next time better be a home run.
Bet it's gonna stay that way for a while. Rare breed – mercs like you. Contract's closed, already flicked the eds your way.
